---
// Testimonials Component
---
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/components/testimonials.css">

<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">
                Apa Kata <span class="gradient-text">Pelanggan Pertama Kami</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="section-description">
                Kepercayaan Anda adalah prioritas utama kami. Berikut adalah beberapa pengalaman nyata dari para developer dan profesional yang telah kami layani.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonials-grid">

            <div class="testimonial-card card animate-fade-in-up">
                <div class="testimonial-header">
                    <div class="author-avatar">
                        <div class="avatar-placeholder">
                            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M20 21V19A4 4 0 0 0 16 15H8A4 4 0 0 0 4 19V21" stroke="var(--accent-green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" stroke="var(--accent-green)" stroke-width="2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4 class="author-name">Andi P.</h4>
                        <p class="author-title">Backend Developer, Jakarta</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <div class="stars">
                            <span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <blockquote class="testimonial-content">
                    "Proses aktivasinya beneran cepet dan gampang banget. Kurang dari 5 menit setelah bayar, undangan GitHub Copilot Enterprise udah masuk ke email. Prosesnya resmi via invite, jadi terasa aman. Recommended seller!"
                </blockquote>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card card animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="testimonial-header">
                    <div class="author-avatar">
                        <div class="avatar-placeholder">
                            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path d="M20 21V19A4 4 0 0 0 16 15H8A4 4 0 0 0 4 19V21" stroke="var(--accent-green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                                <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" stroke="var(--accent-green)" stroke-width="2"/>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <h4 class="author-name">Rina S.</h4>
                        <p class="author-title">Mahasiswi TI, Bandung</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <div class="stars">
                            <span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span><span class="star filled">★</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <blockquote class="testimonial-content">
                    "Awalnya ragu karena harganya jauh lebih murah dari official store. Tapi setelah tanya-tanya via WA, adminnya ramah dan ngejelasin dengan sabar. ExpressVPN langsung aktif dan aman. Sangat worth it!"
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            
            </div>

        </div>
</section>
<style>
	.testimonials {
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.02) 50%, transparent 100%);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.testimonials::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 20%;
		right: -10%;
		width: 400px;
		height: 400px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(60px);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.testimonials::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 20%;
		left: -10%;
		width: 300px;
		height: 300px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(60px);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.testimonials-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.testimonial-card {
		position: relative;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.testimonial-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
		border-radius: 12px;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
	}

	.testimonial-card:hover::before {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	.testimonial-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.author-avatar {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.avatar-placeholder {
		width: 60px;
		height: 60px;
		background: rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.1);
		border: 2px solid rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.3);
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.author-info {
		flex: 1;
	}

	.author-name {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}

	.author-title {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.rating {
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.stars {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2px;
	}

	.star {
		color: rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.3);
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		transition: color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.star.filled {
		color: var(--accent-green);
		text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.5);
	}

	.testimonial-content {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-style: italic;
		position: relative;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.testimonial-content::before {
		content: '"';
		font-size: 4rem;
		color: var(--accent-green);
		opacity: 0.3;
		position: absolute;
		top: -1rem;
		left: -0.5rem;
		font-family: Georgia, serif;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	/* Testimonial Stats */
	.testimonial-stats {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2rem;
		backdrop-filter: var(--blur-backdrop);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.stats-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.stat-item {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.stat-icon {
		width: 64px;
		height: 64px;
		background: rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.1);
		border: 1px solid rgba(50, 205, 50, 0.3);
		border-radius: 16px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.stat-content {
		flex: 1;
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--accent-green);
		line-height: 1;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.stat-label {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-weight: 500;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.testimonials-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.stats-container {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.testimonial-stats {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}

		.stat-item {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.stat-icon {
			width: 48px;
			height: 48px;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.stats-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.testimonial-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			text-align: center;
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}

		.avatar-placeholder {
			width: 48px;
			height: 48px;
		}

		.testimonial-content::before {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
